## Why This Is Asked
Assesses ability to design modular, scalable NLP systems that evolve without full retraining, while meeting strict latency and privacy constraints across multiple languages.

## Key Concepts
- Adapter-based fine-tuning
- Multilingual encoders
- Real-time latency requirements
- Privacy-preserving logging
- Canary rollout and drift detection

## Code Example
```javascript
// Example of adding an adapter for a new intent using adapters
const tokenizer = loadTokenizer("xlm-roberta-base");
const model = loadModelWithHeads("xlm-roberta-base");
model.addAdapter("refund_policy_update");
model.trainAdapter("refund_policy_update");
// fine-tune with a few hundred examples
```

